{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"In my industry,"},{"time":2000,"text":"we believe that images can change the world."},{"time":5000,"text":"Okay, we're naive, we're bright-eyed and bushy-tailed."},{"time":8000,"text":"The truth is that we know that the"},{"time":10000,"text":"images themselves don't change the world,"},{"time":12000,"text":"but we're also aware that, since the beginning of photography,"},{"time":15000,"text":"images have provoked reactions in people,"},{"time":18000,"text":"and those reactions have caused change to happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21000,"text":"So let's begin with a group of images."},{"time":24000,"text":"I'd be extremely surprised"},{"time":26000,"text":"if you didn't recognize many or most of them."},{"time":29000,"text":"They're best described as iconic:"},{"time":31000,"text":"so iconic, perhaps, they're cliches."},{"time":34000,"text":"In fact, they're so well-known"},{"time":36000,"text":"that you might even recognize them"},{"time":38000,"text":"in a slightly or somewhat different form."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":45000,"text":"But I think we're looking for something more."},{"time":47000,"text":"We're looking for something more."},{"time":49000,"text":"We're looking for images that shine"},{"time":51000,"text":"an uncompromising light on crucial issues,"},{"time":54000,"text":"images that transcend borders, that transcend religions,"},{"time":57000,"text":"images that provoke us"},{"time":59000,"text":"to step up and do something --"},{"time":61000,"text":"in other words, to act."},{"time":63000,"text":"Well, this image you've all seen."},{"time":66000,"text":"It changed our view of the physical world."},{"time":68000,"text":"We had never seen our planet from this perspective before."},{"time":71000,"text":"Many people credit"},{"time":73000,"text":"a lot of the birth of the environmental movement"},{"time":75000,"text":"to our seeing the planet like this"},{"time":77000,"text":"for the first time --"},{"time":79000,"text":"its smallness, its fragility."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82000,"text":"Forty years later, this group, more than most,"},{"time":85000,"text":"are well aware of the destructive power"},{"time":87000,"text":"that our species can wield over our environment."},{"time":90000,"text":"And at last, we appear to be doing something about it."},{"time":94000,"text":"This destructive power takes many different forms."},{"time":97000,"text":"For example, these images taken by Brent Stirton"},{"time":100000,"text":"in the Congo."},{"time":102000,"text":"These gorillas were murdered, some would even say crucified,"},{"time":105000,"text":"and unsurprisingly,"},{"time":107000,"text":"they sparked international outrage."},{"time":109000,"text":"Most recently,"},{"time":111000,"text":"we've been tragically reminded of the destructive power of nature itself"},{"time":114000,"text":"with the recent earthquake in Haiti."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117000,"text":"Well, I think what is far worse"},{"time":120000,"text":"is man's destructive power over man."},{"time":122000,"text":"Samuel Pisar, an Auschwitz survivor, said,"},{"time":125000,"text":"and I'll quote him,"},{"time":127000,"text":"\"The Holocaust teaches us that nature,"},{"time":129000,"text":"even in its cruelest moments,"},{"time":132000,"text":"is benign in comparison with man,"},{"time":135000,"text":"when he loses his moral compass and his reason.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":138000,"text":"There's another kind of crucifixion."},{"time":141000,"text":"The horrifying images from Abu Ghraib"},{"time":143000,"text":"as well as the images from Guantanamo"},{"time":145000,"text":"had a profound impact."},{"time":147000,"text":"The publication of those images,"},{"time":149000,"text":"as opposed to the images themselves,"},{"time":151000,"text":"caused a government to change its policies."},{"time":154000,"text":"Some would argue that it is those images"},{"time":156000,"text":"that did more to fuel the insurgency in Iraq"},{"time":159000,"text":"than virtually any other single act."},{"time":161000,"text":"Furthermore, those images forever removed"},{"time":164000,"text":"the so-called moral high ground of the occupying forces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167000,"text":"Let's go back a little."},{"time":169000,"text":"In the 1960s and 1970s,"},{"time":171000,"text":"the Vietnam War was basically shown"},{"time":173000,"text":"in America's living rooms day in, day out."},{"time":175000,"text":"News photos brought people face to face"},{"time":178000,"text":"with the victims of the war: a little girl burned by napalm,"},{"time":182000,"text":"a student killed by the National Guard"},{"time":184000,"text":"at Kent State University in Ohio during a protest."},{"time":187000,"text":"In fact, these images became"},{"time":189000,"text":"the voices of protest themselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191000,"text":"Now, images have power"},{"time":193000,"text":"to shed light of understanding"},{"time":195000,"text":"on suspicion, ignorance,"},{"time":197000,"text":"and in particular -- I've given a lot of talks on this"},{"time":199000,"text":"but I'll just show one image --"},{"time":202000,"text":"the issue of HIV/AIDS."},{"time":205000,"text":"In the 1980s, the stigmatization of people with the disease"},{"time":208000,"text":"was an enormous barrier"},{"time":210000,"text":"to even discussing or addressing it."},{"time":212000,"text":"A simple act, in 1987, of the most famous woman in the world,"},{"time":215000,"text":"the Princess of Wales, touching"},{"time":217000,"text":"an HIV/AIDS infected baby"},{"time":219000,"text":"did a great deal, especially in Europe, to stop that."},{"time":222000,"text":"She, better than most, knew the power of an image."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226000,"text":"So when we are confronted by a powerful image,"},{"time":228000,"text":"we all have a choice:"},{"time":230000,"text":"We can look away, or we can address the image."},{"time":233000,"text":"Thankfully, when these photos appeared in"},{"time":235000,"text":"The Guardian in 1998,"},{"time":237000,"text":"they put a lot of focus and attention and, in the end, a lot of money"},{"time":240000,"text":"towards the Sudan famine relief efforts."},{"time":242000,"text":"Did the images change the world?"},{"time":244000,"text":"No, but they had a major impact."},{"time":247000,"text":"Images often push us to question our core beliefs"},{"time":249000,"text":"and our responsibilities to each other."},{"time":252000,"text":"We all saw those images after Katrina,"},{"time":254000,"text":"and I think for millions of people"},{"time":256000,"text":"they had a very strong impact."},{"time":258000,"text":"And I think it's very unlikely"},{"time":260000,"text":"that they were far from the minds of Americans"},{"time":262000,"text":"when they went to vote in November 2008."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266000,"text":"Unfortunately, some very important images"},{"time":269000,"text":"are deemed too graphic or disturbing for us to see them."},{"time":273000,"text":"I'll show you one photo here,"},{"time":275000,"text":"and it's a photo by Eugene Richards of an Iraq War veteran"},{"time":278000,"text":"from an extraordinary piece of work,"},{"time":280000,"text":"which has never been published, called War Is Personal."},{"time":283000,"text":"But images don't need to be graphic"},{"time":285000,"text":"in order to remind us of the tragedy of war."},{"time":287000,"text":"John Moore set up this photo at Arlington Cemetery."},{"time":290000,"text":"After all the tense moments of conflict"},{"time":292000,"text":"in all the conflict zones of the world,"},{"time":295000,"text":"there's one photograph from a much quieter place"},{"time":298000,"text":"that haunts me still, much more than the others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302000,"text":"Ansel Adams said, and I'm going to disagree with him,"},{"time":305000,"text":"\"You don't take a photograph, you make it.\""},{"time":308000,"text":"In my view, it's not the photographer who makes the photo,"},{"time":310000,"text":"it's you."},{"time":312000,"text":"We bring to each image"},{"time":314000,"text":"our own values, our own belief systems,"},{"time":316000,"text":"and as a result of that, the image resonates with us."},{"time":319000,"text":"My company has 70 million images."},{"time":321000,"text":"I have one image in my office."},{"time":324000,"text":"Here it is."},{"time":326000,"text":"I hope that the next time you see"},{"time":328000,"text":"an image that sparks something in you,"},{"time":330000,"text":"you'll better understand why,"},{"time":332000,"text":"and I know that speaking to this audience,"},{"time":335000,"text":"you'll definitely do something about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337000,"text":"And thank you to all the photographers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}